Entry Point
===========

 - http://127.0.0.3:60080/demo/thruk/ (haproxy loadbalancer)
 - Login is omdadmin / omd

Setup
=====

 - 3 clustered thruk nodes based on the thruk/ folder, not scalable using fixed nodes
 - 1 haproxy load balancer
 - 2 docker volumes etc/ and var/ used for the thruk cluster
 - 1 omd site used as backend for the thruk nodes
